original:
Intensity of lens magnification effect applied on optics with magnification greater than x1.
It aims to emulate the PiP (picture in picture) effect.

The position may not be very accurate while moving with certain weapons

original:
DEPRECATED
Use at your own discretion.

Deadzone allows the camera to stay still while aiming.
Very popular in old style shooter.

NOTE: when using deadzone, even if it doesn't seem so, you will still get all the deficits such as increased recoil, weapon inertia etc.
